        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-03-29 23:07:47.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(8 comments)\n\nAs a general comment: this will generate a bunch of new sonar issues.  Should we merge and deal with those in another JIRA?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "2e842161ae1a23e809508ee3e3ea6d409e525e36",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 477,
          "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
          "username": "jhh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-04-01 15:03:08.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nFor *new code*, comments should be addressed before merged, either discussed and reach an agreement with with the reviewer or address them in code.   For *existing code*, the comment is not binding, it does not need to be addressed at the time of review, but the contributor should consider it for future work, perhaps track it under a jira ticket.   There should also be junit code coverage for new functionality added.  The inspection is lacking tests.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "2a4141d3c9c73aeac1407719e51ae25ba156c5d9",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 1725,
          "name": "Utkarsh Jauhari",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "uj426b@att.com",
          "username": "uj426b"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-04-01 15:04:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nDiscussed with Jim Hahn offline, he is OK to get this merged for now.\nPam, can you please merge this.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "56f37f1e089cf050ba13ad14340fbb6242c67d09",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 57,
          "name": "Pamela Dragosh",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "pd1248@att.com",
          "username": "pdragosh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-04-01 15:09:47.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-2\n\nFolks, let's be aware of ONAP standards for code development. I don't care if something is \"old\" code or was done by someone no longer with the company. Unless folks don't set a higher standard for development, then we will continue to get unsatisfactory code pushed.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
